@page
@model HelpModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Help";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Welcome to the eShopOnWeb Help page! Here you can find information about how to use our online store.</p>

<h2>Getting Started</h2>
<p>Browse our catalog of products, add items to your shopping basket, and proceed to checkout when you're ready to purchase.</p>

<h2>Account Management</h2>
<p>Create an account to track your orders, manage your profile, and save your preferences.</p>

<h2>Shopping Guide</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Use the filters to find products by brand and type</li>
    <li>Click on products to view detailed information</li>
    <li>Add items to your basket using the "ADD TO BASKET" button</li>
    <li>Review your basket and proceed to checkout</li>
</ul>

<h2>Need More Help?</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>